title: Help meeeee does anyone in the world know what this typface is?
content:
Hey everyone, I am thinking that this typeface has been specially produced, but if you guys can tell me that I am wrong and let me know what typeface this is I would be eternally grateful and my nightmare would be over :-)

comments.content: You'll need to reload your image, Typophile.com is assuming it's corrupt or something.

Well, I dont really recognize that font but, quarterround is pretty similar.

It's free and you can get it from [www.dafont.com](http://web.archive.org/web/20131020080510/http:/www.dafont.com/ "www.dafont.com")
